<div class="homev2" id="homev2"><div class="hv-bg" id="hvbg"></div><div class="hv-decor"><span class="orb"></span><span class="ring"></span><span class="leaf"></span><span class="line"></span></div><div class="hv-obj"><div id="gym" class="gym none"></div></div><header class="hv-nav"><a href="{{ '/en/' | url }}" class="hv-brand"><img src="{{ site.logoUrl | url }}" alt="{{ site.name }}"><span>{{ site.name }}</span></a><nav class="hv-links"><a href="#services">Services</a><a href="#plans">Plans</a><a href="#contact">Contact</a><a href="{{ site.googleForm }}">Start Now</a></nav></header><main class="hv-main">
<section class="scene hero" data-bg="forest" data-obj="none"><div><span class="kicker">{{ pages.home.en.hero.badge }}</span><h1>{{ pages.home.en.hero.title_line1 }} {{ pages.home.en.hero.title_line2_gradient }}</h1><p>{{ pages.home.en.hero.description }}</p><a class="btn" href="{{ site.googleForm }}">{{ pages.home.en.hero.cta_primary }}</a></div></section>
<section class="scene" data-bg="waterfall" data-obj="bottle"><div class="split"><article class="panel glass"><span class="kicker">The full system</span><h2>{{ pages.home.en.pillars.title }}</h2><p>{{ pages.home.en.seo.description }}</p><p>All real O2F services, plans, results and contact routes are rebuilt here as one cinematic visual journey.</p></article><div class="photo glass"><img src="{{ site.heroImage | url }}" alt="{{ site.owner }}"><div class="stats"><span>{{ site.stats.years }}<br><small>Experience</small></span><span>{{ site.stats.clients }}<br><small>Clients</small></span><span>{{ site.stats.custom }}<br><small>Plans</small></span><span>{{ site.stats.support }}<br><small>Support</small></span></div></div></div></section>
<section class="scene" id="services" data-bg="forest" data-obj="dumbbell"><div class="services"><div><span class="kicker">{{ pages.services.en.hero.kicker }}</span><h2>{{ pages.services.en.hero.description }}</h2><p>{{ pages.services.en.seo.description }}</p></div><div class="orbit"><div class="core glass"><b>{{ site.owner }}</b></div>{% for service in pages.services.en.services %}<article class="node card glass"><span class="kicker">{{ service.id }}</span><h3>{{ service.title }}</h3><p>{{ service.description }}</p></article>{% endfor %}</div></div></section>
<section class="scene" data-bg="valley" data-obj="kettle"><div class="diagnostic"><div class="radar glass"></div><div><span class="kicker">{{ pages.home.en.pillars.kicker }}</span><h2>{{ pages.home.en.pillars.title }}</h2><div class="readouts">{% for item in pages.home.en.pillars.items %}<div class="readout glass"><b>{{ item.title }}</b><p>{{ item.text }}</p></div>{% endfor %}</div></div></div></section>
<section class="scene" data-bg="mist" data-obj="rope"><div class="journey"><article class="step glass panel"><span>01</span><h3>Assess</h3><p>Current level, case, food preferences and lifestyle load.</p></article><article class="step glass panel"><span>02</span><h3>Build</h3><p>Training, nutrition and guidance are combined.</p></article><article class="step glass panel"><span>03</span><h3>Follow</h3><p>Weekly check-ins keep the plan adjustable.</p></article><article class="step glass panel"><span>04</span><h3>Upgrade</h3><p>The system evolves as the body responds.</p></article></div></section>
<section class="scene" data-bg="waterfall" data-obj="bottle"><div class="gallery">{% for item in pages.home.en.what_you_get.items %}<article class="card glass"><span class="kicker">Output 0{{ loop.index }}</span><h3>{{ item.title }}</h3><p>{{ item.text }}</p></article>{% endfor %}</div></section>
<section class="scene" id="plans" data-bg="forest" data-obj="dumbbell"><div class="plans"><div><span class="kicker">{{ pages.home.en.plans_section.kicker }}</span><h2>{{ pages.home.en.plans_section.title }}</h2><p>Plans are displayed as clear cinematic levels using the real pricing and features.</p></div><div class="terrain">{% for key in ["basic","standard","advanced"] %}{% set p=plans[key] %}<a class="plan glass" href="{{ ('/en/plans/' + p.slug + '/') | url }}"><span class="kicker">{{ "Most popular" if p.highlight else "Access level" }}</span><h3>{{ p.en.name }}</h3><p>{{ p.en.blurb }}</p><div class="price"><div><span>1 month</span><b>{{ p.pricing.egypt.m1.amount }} {{ p.pricing.egypt.m1.currency }}</b></div><div><span>3 months</span><b>{{ p.pricing.egypt.m3.amount }} {{ p.pricing.egypt.m3.currency }}/mo</b></div><div><span>6 months</span><b>{{ p.pricing.egypt.m6.amount }} {{ p.pricing.egypt.m6.currency }}/mo</b></div></div><ul class="features">{% for feature in p.en.features %}{% if loop.index <= 5 %}<li>{{ feature }}</li>{% endif %}{% endfor %}</ul></a>{% endfor %}</div></div></section>
<section class="scene" data-bg="valley" data-obj="kettle"><div class="proof">{% for item in pages.home.en.results.items %}<div class="signal glass"><div><span class="kicker">Signal</span><strong>{{ item.value }}{{ item.unit }}</strong><p>{{ item.text }}</p></div></div>{% endfor %}</div></section>
<section class="scene" id="contact" data-bg="waterfall" data-obj="bottle"><div class="contact"><article class="panel glass"><span class="kicker">{{ pages.home.en.cta.badge }}</span><h2>{{ pages.home.en.cta.title }}</h2><p>{{ pages.home.en.cta.description }}</p><a class="btn" href="{{ site.googleForm }}">{{ pages.home.en.cta.button }}</a></article><div class="faq"><article class="bubble glass"><b>Is this only training?</b><p>No. It combines training, nutrition and ongoing follow-up.</p></article><article class="bubble glass"><b>Not sure where to start?</b><p>{{ pages.services.en.cta.description }}</p></article><article class="bubble glass"><b>What makes it different?</b><p>It is built around your goals, schedule, lifestyle and health status.</p></article></div></div></section>
</main></div><script>(function(){const root=document.getElementById('homev2'),bg=document.getElementById('hvbg'),gym=document.getElementById('gym'),sc=[...document.querySelectorAll('.scene')],imgs={forest:"url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441974231531-c6227db76b6e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2200&q=85')",waterfall:"url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1432405972618-c60b0225b8f9?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2200&q=85')",valley:"url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2200&q=85')",mist:"url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470252649378-9c29740c9fa8?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2200&q=85')"};function active(){let a=sc[0];sc.forEach(s=>{const r=s.getBoundingClientRect();if(r.top<innerHeight*.56&&r.bottom>innerHeight*.2)a=s});return a}function update(){const p=Math.max(0,Math.min(1,-root.getBoundingClientRect().top/(root.offsetHeight-innerHeight||1))),s=active(),o=s.dataset.obj||'none';bg.style.setProperty('--scene',imgs[s.dataset.bg]||imgs.forest);bg.style.setProperty('--x',(Math.sin(p*5)*24)+'px');bg.style.setProperty('--y',(-p*130)+'px');gym.className='gym '+o+' show';gym.innerHTML=o==='dumbbell'?'<span></span><i></i><span></span>':'';gym.style.setProperty('--ox',(Math.sin(p*8)*32)+'px');gym.style.setProperty('--oy',(Math.cos(p*5)*-16)+'px')}addEventListener('scroll',update,{passive:true});addEventListener('resize',update);update()})();</script>
